race.comment: SMART AND MIGHTY (2) has placed two of six but rarely far away and has run two very good races for the claimer Alice Kennedy. Looks well placed here off the low draw and will give a sight in this company. BRING THE THUNDER (11) has raced twice to date and finished seventh at each. This is easier and has the blinkers added. Will take stopping. WAYNE'S DREAM (10) was placed this trip two back then came through a very strong form race at Wangaratta last time. This sharper trip suits and is worth another chance. DO SAY (5) is resuming in easier company and on her debut run in stakes class when fourth would be good enough for this.
